                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "3CPRIMP"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " External Target Facility (ETF)"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "FRAGM"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A primary beam of 18O was accelerated to 280",
                "MeV/nucleon by the main Cooler Storage Ring (CSRm)",
                "synchrotron of the Heavy Ion Research Facility in",
                "Lanzhou (HIRFL) and directed onto a Be target of 15 mm",
                "thickness. The unstable secondary beams produced",
                "by fragmentation of 18O were separated using the",
                "Radioactive Ion Beam Line in Lanzhou-II (RIBLL2) and",
                "transported to the experimental area where the ETF is",
                "located."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 900 mg/cm2 thick carbon target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The acceptance of the ETF detector system for the 15B",
                "fragments amounted to about 100%. The detection",
                "efficiency of the ETF was calibrated using the",
                "various secondary beams, and the derived efficiencies",
                "were 80%-90%, depending on the charge number of the",
                "beam particles."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN",
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The time of flight was measured between",
                "two plastic scintillator detectors (SC1 and SC2) and",
                "the energy loss was recorded by a multiple sampling",
                "ionization chamber (MUSIC1). The time of flight was",
                "measured between a plastic scintillator (SC2) and a",
                "30-strip plastic scintillator wall (TOFW) placed",
                "about 10 m downstream from the target. The energy",
                "loss was measured by a multiple sampling ionization",
                "chamber (MUSIC2) placed 50 cm downstream of the",
                "reaction target."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWDC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two multiwire drift chambers, located upstream",
                "of the carbon target and each having an active area",
                "of 13 x 13 cm2, were used to measure the trajectories",
                "of the incoming particles. The magnetic rigidity of",
                "the outgoing charged fragments passing through the",
                "ETF magnet was reconstructed from the positions",
                "measured using two MWDCs placed upstream and three",
                "MWDCs placed downstream of the magnet. The two MWDCs",
                "placed upstream of the magnet have an active area of",
                "13 x 13 cm2. Each of the three MWDCs downstream of",
                "the magnet has an active area of 80 x 60 cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The secondary cocktail beams, magnetically",
                "centered on 16C, were identified using the TOF-dE",
                "method."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The trigger of the data acquisition system",
                "was generated only by requiring the coincidence of",
                "the signals from SC1 and SC2, both in front of the",
                "reaction target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To avoid effects arising from reactions on the target",
                "frame, the beam-spot size on the target was limited",
                "to 4 cm in diameter in the off-line analysis by",
                "setting a software gate using the information from",
                "the MWDCs. The background contributions were measured",
                "by using target-out runs and subtracted."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainties are dominated by",
                "statistical errors, while systematic errors mainly",
                "arise from the correction for the ETF detection",
                "efficiency and are added to the statistical",
                "uncertainty in quadrature."
              ]
            }
          ],
